    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Updated, replaced `.Single` with `.First` in the armament look-up.\r\n\r\nEven ignoring performance, it is entirely possible that mods might want to 'share' an attack anim between two armaments (for example, dual-barreled units might need two armaments to fire from both barrels at the same time, imagine TS Wolverine firing visible projectiles), so being forced to give one of the armaments a different name just to avoid a crash is a bit inconvenient."
  },
